                            </decoNote>
                        </decoDesc>
                        <bindingDesc>
                            <binding contemporary="true">
                                <p>Original late medieval binding. Light brown leather over wooden boards. Five raised bands on the <locus from="Spine" to="Spine" scheme="other"/>. Two bosses of bone (traces of a third) on <locus from="RCO" to="RCO" scheme="other"/>. Metal catches remaining on <locus from="LCO" to="LCO" scheme="other"/> and <locus from="RCO" to="RCO" scheme="other"/>.</p>
                                <p>
